sentences.sentence: The main estimation is the rugosity and the linear rugosity of the fracture surface. A set of theoretical models has been built.
sentences.translation: 评价的主要内容集中在裂隙面粗糙度和线粗糙度方面，并建立了一系列的理论模型。
